OL,3,CSecond US pilot rescued after Iran
OL,4,Cdowned fighter jet, Trump says
OL,6,FThe second US military pilot who went
OL,7,Fmissing after Iran shot down a fighter
OL,8,Fjet has been rescued, President Donald
OL,9,FTrump has said.
OL,11,FA frantic US search-and-rescue
OL,12,Foperation was launched after an F-15E
OL,13,FStrike Eagle jet crashed on Friday, as
OL,14,FIran also offered a reward for anyone
OL,15,Fwho handed in the "enemy pilot".
OL,26,@wD@SOUwD@_O]
