PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775466313
OL,3,CSecond US pilot rescued after Iran
OL,4,Cdowned fighter jet, Trump says
OL,6,FTrump announced the rescue in a social
OL,7,Fmedia post early on Sunday, and said:
OL,8,F"This brave Warrior was behind enemy
OL,9,Flines in the treacherous mountains of
OL,10,FIran, being hunted down by our
OL,11,Fenemies, who were getting closer and
OL,12,Fcloser by the hour."
OL,14,FAnother military pilot was rescued
OL,15,Fearlier on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775466313
OL,3,CSecond US pilot rescued after Iran
OL,4,Cdowned fighter jet, Trump says
OL,6,FTrump said that the pilot is injured
OL,7,Fbut "will be just fine," adding that
OL,8,Fthe rescue involved "dozens of
OL,9,Faircraft" and that the US had been
OL,10,Fmonitoring his location "24 hours a
OL,11,Fday, and diligently planning for his
OL,12,Frescue."
OL,14,FThe fighter jet was the first US
OL,15,Faircraft to crash in Iranian territory
OL,16,Fsince the conflict began in late
OL,17,FFebruary.
OL,19,FTrump said last week the US had
OL,20,F"decimated" Iran and would finish the
OL,21,Fwar "very fast".
