OL,3,CSecond US pilot rescued after Iran
OL,4,Cdowned fighter jet, Trump says
OL,6,FTwo days later, Iran shot down two US
OL,7,Fmilitary aircraft, showing the risks
OL,8,Fof the US military campaign and Iran's
OL,9,Fability to continue striking back
OL,10,Fdespite being weakened.
OL,12,FThe conflict began with joint US-
OL,13,FIsrael strikes against Iran on
OL,14,FFebruary 28 and has killed thousands,
OL,15,Fshaken global markets, disrupted key
OL,16,Fshipping routes and driven up fuel
OL,17,Fprices.
OL,19,FBoth sides have targeted civilian
OL,20,Fareas, raising concerns about
OL,21,Fpotential war crimes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
