OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775466313
OL,3,CSecond US pilot rescued after Iran
OL,4,Cdowned fighter jet, Trump says
OL,6,FThe other aircraft downed was a US A-
OL,7,F10 attack plane. The condition of its
OL,8,Fcrew and the exact crash location were
OL,9,Fnot immediately known.
OL,11,FTrump renews threat
OL,13,FTrump has renewed his threat to Iran
OL,14,Fto reopen the Strait of Hormuz, a key
OL,15,Fglobal shipping route that has been
OL,16,Fblocked by Tehran, warning that there
OL,17,Fwill be severe consequences if it is
OL,18,Fnot reopened by Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
