OL,3,CSecond US pilot rescued after Iran
OL,4,Cdowned fighter jet, Trump says
OL,6,FIn a social media post on Saturday, he
OL,7,Fwrote: "Remember when I gave Iran ten
OL,8,Fdays to MAKE A DEAL or OPEN UP THE
OL,9,FHORMUZ STRAIT. Time is running out -
OL,10,F48 hours before all Hell will reign
OL,11,Fdown on them."
OL,13,FIran responded with its own warning,
OL,14,Fwith General Ali Abdollahi Aliabadi
OL,15,Fsaying on late Saturday the "doors of
OL,16,Fhell will be opened to you" if the
OL,17,Fcountry's infrastructure is attacked,
OL,18,Fand threatening US military
OL,19,Finfrastructure in the region.
