OL,3,CSecond US pilot rescued after Iran
OL,4,Cdowned fighter jet, Trump says
OL,6,FDespite the escalation, diplomatic
OL,7,Fefforts are continuing.
OL,9,FPakistan's Foreign Ministry
OL,10,Fspokesperson, Tahir Andrab, said its
OL,11,Fattempts to broker a ceasefire were
OL,12,F"right on track, with talks expected
OL,13,Fto be hosted between the US and Iran
OL,14,Fsoon.
OL,16,FRegional mediators, including
OL,17,FPakistan, Turkey and Egypt, are
OL,18,Fworking to bring both sides to the
OL,19,Fnegotiating table, with proposals
OL,20,Fincluding a pause in fighting to allow
OL,21,Ffor a diplomatic settlement.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
