OL,3,CSecond US pilot rescued after Iran
OL,4,Cdowned fighter jet, Trump says
OL,6,FMeanwhile, a second US military
OL,7,Faircraft went down in the Middle East
OL,8,Fon Friday, according to a US official,
OL,9,Falthough it remains unclear whether it
OL,10,Fcrashed or was shot down, or if Iran
OL,11,Fwas involved.
OL,13,FIranian state media reported that a US
OL,14,FA-10 attack aircraft had crashed in
OL,15,Fthe Persian Gulf after being hit by
OL,16,FIranian defences.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
