OL,3,CSecond US pilot rescued after Iran
OL,4,Cdowned fighter jet, Trump says
OL,6,FThe Bab el-Mandeb Strait
OL,8,FIran has also threatened it could
OL,9,Fdisrupt another major shipping route,
OL,10,Fthe Bab el-Mandeb Strait, which links
OL,11,Fthe Red Sea to the Gulf of Aden.
OL,13,FIt makes up more than a tenth of the
OL,14,Fworld's seaborne oil, along with a
OL,15,Fquarter of global container shipping.
OL,17,FThe conflict has killed more than
OL,18,F1,900 people in Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
