OL,3,CSecond US pilot rescued after Iran
OL,4,Cdowned fighter jet, Trump says
OL,6,FElsewhere, more than two dozen people
OL,7,Fhave died in Gulf Arab states and the
OL,8,Foccupied West Bank, 19 in Israel, and
OL,9,F13 US soldiers.
OL,11,FIn Lebanon, more than 1,400 people
OL,12,Fhave been killed and over one million
OL,13,Fdisplaced, with 10 Israeli soldiers
OL,14,Falso reported dead.
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
